text: ['3.1.3  Bindings', '3.13.  Gabon has bound all its tariff lines at a ceiling of 60% for agricultural products; and 15% for non-agricultural products, with the exception of a few tariff lines bound at 60%. The average bound rate is 22%.', '3.14.  "Other duties and taxes" are bound at a ceiling of 150%.', "3.15.  For  2,058  tariff  lines  (38.6%  of  Gabon's  tariff),  the  applied  rates  are  still  higher  than the bound  rates.  This  is  the  case  for  many  non-agricultural  products  in  particular,  for  which the applicable  rates  are  either  20%  or  30%,  thus  higher  than  the  bound  rate  of  15%. The authorities are currently taking steps to renegotiate them.", '13 CEMAC Customs Code.', '\x0cWT/TPR/S/285 • GABON', '- 274 -']
